1
00:00:00,890 --> 00:00:03,440
Lily, you saved my life.

2
00:00:04,340 --> 00:00:06,560
I am glad I was able to 
protect your homeland...

3
00:00:08,360 --> 00:00:10,140
Thank you very much...

4
00:00:10,900 --> 00:00:12,010
...Prince.

5
00:00:22,890 --> 00:00:23,910
Black cat!

6
00:00:26,320 --> 00:00:28,500
Lily!

7
00:02:03,100 --> 00:02:04,430
Prince...

8
00:02:04,840 --> 00:02:06,430
Lily!

9
00:02:11,440 --> 00:02:13,400
Traitor.

10
00:02:13,400 --> 00:02:16,570
In the end, you are one of 
the Fallen. Just an Exceed.

11
00:02:17,050 --> 00:02:20,700
You've forgotten the debt you owe our king for 
saving you, and instead turn your blade against him.

12
00:02:21,420 --> 00:02:23,000
It's the other Erza!

13
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:24,780
Her name is Knightwalker.

14
00:02:25,530 --> 00:02:26,760
Lily!

15
00:02:26,760 --> 00:02:28,710
How dare you!

16
00:02:30,960 --> 00:02:32,760
Dragon Sense!

17
00:02:35,220 --> 00:02:37,970
S-Someone save Lily!

18
00:02:37,970 --> 00:02:39,610
You mustn't, Chagot!

19
00:02:40,010 --> 00:02:43,080
Queen, leave him to me!

20
00:02:44,310 --> 00:02:46,520
Scarlet!

21
00:02:47,340 --> 00:02:48,900
So heavy...

22
00:02:48,900 --> 00:02:50,350
Knightwalker...

23
00:02:50,350 --> 00:02:51,400
Wait, Erza.

24
00:02:53,340 --> 00:02:59,650
You intend to aim your spear at me, the 
Prince of Edolas, Erza Knightwalker?

25
00:02:59,650 --> 00:03:00,810
Prince?

26
00:03:07,870 --> 00:03:11,550
Prince, you say? Don't make me laugh!

27
00:03:11,550 --> 00:03:15,310
I don't think of you as my son!

28
00:03:16,040 --> 00:03:17,590
That's the voice of the King!

29
00:03:18,220 --> 00:03:19,580
Where is he?

30
00:03:19,580 --> 00:03:25,470
After 7 years of hiding in faraway lands, 
you have some nerve skulking back here!

31
00:03:26,800 --> 00:03:32,250
I know that you've been going around 
Earthland sealing off Anima!

32
00:03:32,250 --> 00:03:33,830
You've betrayed your country!

33
00:03:33,830 --> 00:03:36,720
You sold out your own kingdom!

34
00:03:36,720 --> 00:03:38,720
Where is that voice coming from?

35
00:03:38,720 --> 00:03:41,660
It's like it's coming from 
deep inside the ground...

36
00:03:41,660 --> 00:03:43,890
Hey! Show yourself!

37
00:03:43,890 --> 00:03:45,350
Yeah!

38
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:48,960
Your Anima plan was a failure.

39
00:03:48,960 --> 00:03:51,370
Continuing to fight would 
be meaningless, yes?

40
00:03:51,740 --> 00:03:55,250
Meaning? The meaning of fighting?

41
00:03:58,230 --> 00:04:02,180
What's that noise? Or wait, what is...

42
00:04:02,180 --> 00:04:04,410
The air is trembling from magic power!

43
00:04:05,220 --> 00:04:07,890
This is not a fight.

44
00:04:07,890 --> 00:04:11,070
It is retaliation against 
those who defy the King!

45
00:04:11,310 --> 00:04:14,270
A one-sided extermination!

46
00:04:17,670 --> 00:04:19,000
What is that?

47
00:04:19,500 --> 00:04:21,070
Some magical weapon?

48
00:04:22,310 --> 00:04:29,170
No matter who stands in my way, 
I will eliminate them. Even you!

49
00:04:29,170 --> 00:04:31,950
There won't be any trace left!

50
00:04:32,640 --> 00:04:33,840
Father...

51
00:04:34,950 --> 00:04:36,420
I am no father.

52
00:04:36,970 --> 00:04:40,140
I am the King of Edolas!

53
00:04:44,310 --> 00:04:47,690
Yes... I'll wipe you out here,

54
00:04:47,690 --> 00:04:51,680
and then no one will be left 
to stop the Anima in Earthland!

55
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:54,340
I'll suck up another giant lacrima,

56
00:04:54,340 --> 00:04:57,000
and then fuse it with the Exceed!

57
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:59,550
I can do it as many times as I want!

58
00:05:00,130 --> 00:05:00,900
That's...

59
00:05:06,480 --> 00:05:09,990
Nothing is impossible for the King!

60
00:05:14,980 --> 00:05:20,500
The King's power is absolute!

61
00:05:25,170 --> 00:05:28,100
That shape... That magic power...

62
00:05:28,480 --> 00:05:30,110
It can be none other!

63
00:05:30,110 --> 00:05:32,430
M-My word...

64
00:05:32,430 --> 00:05:34,780
That's... That's...!

65
00:05:35,020 --> 00:05:37,480
Droma Anim!

66
00:05:37,850 --> 00:05:39,210
Droma Anim?

67
00:05:39,660 --> 00:05:42,190
It means "Dragon Knight" 
in our native tongue.

68
00:05:43,200 --> 00:05:45,520
It's a hardened armored dragon?

69
00:05:46,480 --> 00:05:47,420
A dragon?

70
00:05:48,130 --> 00:05:51,160
Or rather, it's in the shape of one.

71
00:05:51,430 --> 00:05:53,110
Hardened armor?

72
00:05:53,110 --> 00:05:55,120
What does that mean?

73
00:05:55,750 --> 00:05:57,750
Special anti-wizard lacrima...

74
00:05:57,750 --> 00:06:02,200
Wizard cancelers nullify all external magic!

75
00:06:02,200 --> 00:06:03,920
It's a suit of armor you can pilot!

76
00:06:04,450 --> 00:06:08,430
The King's inside of it, 
controlling Droma Anim!

77
00:06:10,750 --> 00:06:14,840
My soldiers... Capture the Exceeds!

78
00:06:14,840 --> 00:06:15,720
Yes, sire!

79
00:06:18,690 --> 00:06:20,990
Crap... Run for it!

80
00:06:22,980 --> 00:06:24,870
Don't run!

81
00:06:24,870 --> 00:06:26,990
Magicalize Cannon is fully charged!

82
00:06:27,220 --> 00:06:28,280
Irradiate them!

83
00:06:37,080 --> 00:06:39,100
Everyone, run!

84
00:06:39,100 --> 00:06:41,830
Chagot... We should get farther away...

85
00:06:42,100 --> 00:06:43,160
Everyone...

86
00:06:44,020 --> 00:06:45,580
Survive!

87
00:06:46,320 --> 00:06:47,940
After them!

88
00:06:50,200 --> 00:06:53,120
We'll protect the Exceeds 
from the Royal Army!

89
00:06:53,120 --> 00:06:55,340
Attack Knightwalker's forces!

90
00:06:55,340 --> 00:06:56,450
Right!

91
00:06:58,000 --> 00:07:01,920
Oh yeah... You don't get queasy 
when riding this Legion...

92
00:07:02,150 --> 00:07:05,630
Did you have Troia cast on you 
to help your motion sickness?

93
00:07:05,630 --> 00:07:06,700
What?!

94
00:07:07,390 --> 00:07:10,020
T-This guy's like one of our buddies, right?

95
00:07:10,020 --> 00:07:12,220
Stop treating it like transportation!

96
00:07:12,220 --> 00:07:13,470
That's cold.

97
00:07:13,470 --> 00:07:15,860
Yeah... Sorry about that.

98
00:07:15,860 --> 00:07:18,500
Man, it's been a long time 
since we did this bit.

99
00:07:18,730 --> 00:07:22,310
Enough pointless banter for now. 
What'll we do about that giant thing?

100
00:07:22,310 --> 00:07:24,200
Don't call it pointless!

101
00:07:24,200 --> 00:07:26,340
It's pointless to even try and face it!

102
00:07:26,340 --> 00:07:28,140
Magic won't work on it!

103
00:07:28,140 --> 00:07:29,760
We just have to dodge it!

104
00:07:30,200 --> 00:07:32,220
The Exceeds are defenseless now!

105
00:07:32,670 --> 00:07:34,600
If we don't protect them, then...

106
00:07:34,600 --> 00:07:36,290
Right! Let's go!

107
00:07:37,700 --> 00:07:40,610
Protect them while dodging me?

108
00:07:43,150 --> 00:07:46,030
I won't let a single human escape!

109
00:07:46,390 --> 00:07:49,560
I'll blast every last one of you to bits!

110
00:07:49,560 --> 00:07:53,860
Begone!!

111
00:07:55,300 --> 00:07:56,660
Mystogan...

112
00:07:56,660 --> 00:08:02,160
Mystogan? Is that your 
name on Earthland, Jellal?

113
00:08:04,160 --> 00:08:06,730
Erza, take this chance and go!

114
00:08:06,730 --> 00:08:07,800
But...

115
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:09,120
Go!

116
00:08:09,120 --> 00:08:10,920
Prince...

117
00:08:10,920 --> 00:08:11,880
You...

118
00:08:11,880 --> 00:08:14,140
Three Layered Magic Circle...

119
00:08:15,090 --> 00:08:16,650
Mirror Water!

120
00:08:19,500 --> 00:08:21,470
What? It's reflecting back?

121
00:08:23,810 --> 00:08:25,060
Did that do it?

122
00:08:25,500 --> 00:08:27,940
Wow! So that's Mystogan...

123
00:08:30,760 --> 00:08:32,450
That tickles!

124
00:08:33,300 --> 00:08:34,880
It didn't even scratch him!

125
00:08:34,880 --> 00:08:36,040
Impossible!

126
00:08:36,040 --> 00:08:37,110
That's...

127
00:08:37,670 --> 00:08:42,030
Exactly! This is the 
power of Wizard Canceler!

128
00:08:42,030 --> 00:08:48,270
No matter what wizard faces it, 
no magic will work on Droma Anim!

129
00:08:55,750 --> 00:08:57,220
Mystogan!

130
00:08:59,860 --> 00:09:02,900
You're much more suited to 
crawling along the ground!

131
00:09:02,900 --> 00:09:06,100
You should wander along the ground 
until you give up and die!

132
00:09:09,440 --> 00:09:11,860
Damn it... Ice Make...

133
00:09:15,190 --> 00:09:16,930
This is pretty tough.

134
00:09:16,930 --> 00:09:18,700
I think I'm gonna be sick, 
and I'm not even Natsu!

135
00:09:18,700 --> 00:09:20,030
Help me!

136
00:09:20,030 --> 00:09:20,870
Monmo!

137
00:09:22,950 --> 00:09:25,430
Ooh, how beautiful.

138
00:09:25,430 --> 00:09:29,060
Turn every Exceed into 
a lacrima. Spare no one!

139
00:09:29,060 --> 00:09:33,320
How dare the humans hide the 
fact they had such a monster?!

140
00:09:34,890 --> 00:09:38,580
The beast that darkens the 
heavens, leading to extinction...

141
00:09:39,700 --> 00:09:43,580
Its name is the Dragon Knight, Droma Anim.

142
00:09:43,950 --> 00:09:51,100
Long, long ago, not only Edolas, but Extalia 
as well came very close to being wiped out.

143
00:09:51,100 --> 00:09:57,780
It was so dangerous, the humans 
should have sealed it themselves.

144
00:09:58,030 --> 00:10:01,620
So what do you mean, almost wiped out?

145
00:10:02,760 --> 00:10:04,870
I don't know the details.

146
00:10:05,730 --> 00:10:07,290
According to the legend,

147
00:10:08,250 --> 00:10:11,540
when the Droma Anim dyed the heavens black,

148
00:10:11,540 --> 00:10:15,250
the world lost more than 
half of its magic power!

149
00:10:18,010 --> 00:10:21,780
Damn it! There's no way we 
can fight while dodging that!

150
00:10:21,780 --> 00:10:23,260
Legipyon, hang in there!

151
00:10:23,260 --> 00:10:25,730
But what should we do?

152
00:10:25,730 --> 00:10:28,610
I think we should use Lucy as a decoy!

153
00:10:28,610 --> 00:10:29,990
You little devil!

154
00:10:29,990 --> 00:10:30,870
You mean cat.

155
00:10:30,870 --> 00:10:33,540
Hey, stop breaking the flow of conversation.

156
00:10:35,320 --> 00:10:36,440
What?

157
00:10:41,350 --> 00:10:47,450
Who? Magic shouldn't work on Droma 
Anim, so who is attacking me?

158
00:10:47,450 --> 00:10:50,540
Roar of the Sky Dragon!

159
00:10:52,500 --> 00:10:55,630
You scum!

160
00:10:58,050 --> 00:11:00,290
Hey, not bad, Wendy.

161
00:11:00,290 --> 00:11:04,760
No... The attacks from the 
two of you did more damage.

162
00:11:04,760 --> 00:11:07,870
Let's do it... How dare 
they do that to my cat?

163
00:11:08,300 --> 00:11:11,770
I see! It's <i>you</i> fools!

164
00:11:12,030 --> 00:11:13,100
Natsu!

165
00:11:13,100 --> 00:11:13,980
Wendy!

166
00:11:14,510 --> 00:11:15,400
Gajeel!

167
00:11:16,750 --> 00:11:19,900
Go on. Protect the cats.

168
00:11:21,360 --> 00:11:23,160
We're counting on things here.

169
00:11:23,540 --> 00:11:27,370
But will just the three of them 
be okay against that thing?

170
00:11:27,370 --> 00:11:29,580
What? Not a problem.

171
00:11:30,980 --> 00:11:35,500
We're up against a dragon. They're 
the only ones who can defeat it.

172
00:11:36,470 --> 00:11:38,500
The dragon-hunting wizards...

173
00:11:39,810 --> 00:11:41,320
Dragon Slayers!

174
00:11:56,790 --> 00:11:59,150
Those are lacrima?

175
00:11:59,150 --> 00:12:01,330
Everyone's turned into a lacrima?

176
00:12:02,180 --> 00:12:03,750
The Dragon Chain has been severed,

177
00:12:03,750 --> 00:12:07,860
and with it was lost a lacrima that could have 
been 10 years of magic power for this kingdom...

178
00:12:08,320 --> 00:12:13,330
Even if all the Exceed are magicalized, 
that won't change the situation.

179
00:12:14,090 --> 00:12:19,380
He even brought out Droma Anim... 
How is this even going to end?

180
00:12:19,380 --> 00:12:21,530
You really shouldn't move!

181
00:12:22,050 --> 00:12:24,350
Lily, you're safe?

182
00:12:27,530 --> 00:12:28,680
Prince!

183
00:12:30,600 --> 00:12:33,820
Hey, hey... Look at those humans!

184
00:12:33,820 --> 00:12:36,140
Just the three of them plan on fighting?

185
00:12:36,140 --> 00:12:37,810
That's nuts!

186
00:12:37,810 --> 00:12:40,100
But kind of cool...

187
00:12:40,100 --> 00:12:42,090
Chagot...

188
00:12:42,090 --> 00:12:45,020
Let us escape to somewhere 
a bit farther away...

189
00:12:45,020 --> 00:12:47,660
If we stay here, we'll get caught up in it!

190
00:12:50,160 --> 00:12:52,160
Let's do this, Salamander.

191
00:12:52,160 --> 00:12:54,480
Teaming up with you, <i>again</i>?

192
00:12:54,480 --> 00:12:56,890
You and I can settle things

193
00:12:56,890 --> 00:13:00,130
after we give this thing 
the bustin' up it deserves.

194
00:13:00,760 --> 00:13:02,130
I'm all fired up.

195
00:13:02,970 --> 00:13:05,630
Foolish children!

196
00:13:06,150 --> 00:13:07,380
I'll provide support!

197
00:13:07,380 --> 00:13:10,850
O swift wind that dashes through the heavens!

198
00:13:13,550 --> 00:13:15,100
W-What's this?

199
00:13:15,650 --> 00:13:18,480
My body... It's light as a feather!

200
00:13:19,220 --> 00:13:20,150
Vernier!

201
00:13:26,110 --> 00:13:27,770
They dodged?

202
00:13:29,590 --> 00:13:30,740
Fast!

203
00:13:32,180 --> 00:13:34,580
I can't set the aim!

204
00:13:34,700 --> 00:13:36,500
Iron Fist of the Fire Dragon!

205
00:13:36,500 --> 00:13:38,490
Pillar of the Iron Dragon!

206
00:13:44,420 --> 00:13:47,340
Magic shouldn't work at all on Droma Anim!

207
00:13:47,920 --> 00:13:51,340
But it's taking damage... Just a tiny bit.

208
00:13:53,310 --> 00:13:56,220
Damn this thing! How hard is it?

209
00:13:56,600 --> 00:13:58,010
We're barely denting it!

210
00:13:58,010 --> 00:13:59,020
In that case...

211
00:13:59,020 --> 00:14:02,570
O strength of arm to cleave the heavens!

212
00:14:06,570 --> 00:14:07,860
What is it this time?

213
00:14:08,530 --> 00:14:09,700
Arms!

214
00:14:11,570 --> 00:14:14,640
Power is welling up inside of me!

215
00:14:14,640 --> 00:14:16,810
It's magic that increases your attack power!

216
00:14:16,810 --> 00:14:18,300
You ain't bad.

217
00:14:21,030 --> 00:14:24,460
What? Their magic power is increasing?

218
00:14:27,570 --> 00:14:29,670
Dazzling Blaze of the Fire Dragon!

219
00:14:29,670 --> 00:14:31,880
Spears of the Iron Dragon! Demon Poles!

220
00:14:34,170 --> 00:14:35,710
How dare you!

221
00:14:35,710 --> 00:14:37,220
It's that little girl!

222
00:14:39,220 --> 00:14:40,970
Launch the Dragon Knight Balls!

223
00:14:44,060 --> 00:14:46,200
Oh, no! Wendy!

224
00:14:46,200 --> 00:14:47,740
I will be fine.

225
00:14:48,290 --> 00:14:49,530
Vernier!

226
00:14:55,450 --> 00:14:56,580
They're homing?

227
00:15:03,130 --> 00:15:04,840
Oww...

228
00:15:14,150 --> 00:15:15,240
Natsu!

229
00:15:16,170 --> 00:15:17,590
I don't think so.

230
00:15:17,590 --> 00:15:19,470
There's more where that came from!

231
00:15:21,910 --> 00:15:23,400
I ain't gonna let you!

232
00:15:24,890 --> 00:15:26,650
So annoying!

233
00:15:29,690 --> 00:15:31,820
There are still 2 left!

234
00:15:31,820 --> 00:15:34,380
Those are... Don't, Natsu-san!

235
00:15:34,380 --> 00:15:36,160
They're different than the ones from before!

236
00:15:50,600 --> 00:15:53,700
You naive, foolish wizards!

237
00:15:53,700 --> 00:15:56,860
And you call yourself dragon hunters?

238
00:15:57,930 --> 00:15:59,220
What the...?

239
00:16:00,500 --> 00:16:03,190
He's <i>eating</i> the Dragon 
Knight Ball's explosion?!

240
00:16:08,600 --> 00:16:11,930
And <i>he's</i> eating my tail!

241
00:16:14,250 --> 00:16:17,240
What's with this awful fire?

242
00:16:17,720 --> 00:16:20,520
I ain't never tasted anything 
that pissed me off more.

243
00:16:23,480 --> 00:16:26,540
That ain't it. But in the meantime...

244
00:16:27,210 --> 00:16:30,300
Now that I've eaten, I'm all revved up!

245
00:16:30,300 --> 00:16:32,410
What the hell do you think you're doing?

246
00:16:32,410 --> 00:16:34,380
You're one real annoying pest.

247
00:16:35,260 --> 00:16:37,220
Nonsense...

248
00:16:37,850 --> 00:16:41,080
These are Earthland wizards...?

249
00:16:41,080 --> 00:16:45,700
Sure is strong. It ain't called 
a "dragon" for nothing.

250
00:16:45,700 --> 00:16:49,890
Give me a break. This ain't 
even close to a dragon!

251
00:16:50,350 --> 00:16:53,820
Even though he's the king of this land, 
he doesn't have a single bodyguard.

252
00:16:53,820 --> 00:16:55,700
He's got incredible self-confidence.

253
00:16:57,520 --> 00:16:59,320
I'm fired up!

254
00:17:00,210 --> 00:17:03,240
These are Dragon Slayers...

255
00:17:06,120 --> 00:17:10,330
However, all the more for me...

256
00:17:11,600 --> 00:17:12,790
What's this?

257
00:17:12,790 --> 00:17:16,550
It's collecting magic power from the air?

258
00:17:17,420 --> 00:17:19,790
It's flowing into that thing?

259
00:17:24,570 --> 00:17:27,060
As long as they're here,

260
00:17:27,060 --> 00:17:30,630
I can put my Anima plan 
into motion once again!

261
00:17:34,640 --> 00:17:38,990
For a future of eternal magic 
power, I will capture these three.

262
00:17:39,490 --> 00:17:42,460
No... They are already dangerous weapons.

263
00:17:42,460 --> 00:17:47,750
No imprisonment... I'll have to break 
them into a couple of pieces each.

264
00:17:49,760 --> 00:17:53,930
First, I will rid everyone 
of the will to fight!

265
00:17:54,420 --> 00:17:58,930
With the Black Heavens power Droma Anim has!

266
00:18:06,680 --> 00:18:08,060
Go!

267
00:18:18,790 --> 00:18:20,670
Did a mosquito just try and bite me?

268
00:18:24,100 --> 00:18:25,220
Natsu-san!

269
00:18:26,000 --> 00:18:28,500
Even with the power of Arms, 
our attacks won't work!

270
00:18:30,740 --> 00:18:34,370
Can you feel this overwhelmingly 
powerful magic?

271
00:18:34,370 --> 00:18:38,630
It is incredible! Don't kneel before 
me! Don't plead for your life!

272
00:18:38,630 --> 00:18:43,010
I want you to just keep standing 
there shaking like leaves!

273
00:18:45,510 --> 00:18:50,260
Be afraid, Dragon Wizards!

274
00:19:02,500 --> 00:19:04,200
I'm sorry, Natsu...

275
00:19:04,670 --> 00:19:05,580
Prince...

276
00:19:06,020 --> 00:19:07,570
What is the meaning of this?

277
00:19:07,830 --> 00:19:10,660
You let yourself be done 
in on purpose before?

278
00:19:14,450 --> 00:19:16,290
In order to save me?

279
00:19:16,570 --> 00:19:18,300
How are your injuries?

280
00:19:18,300 --> 00:19:20,270
This? It's nothing serious.

281
00:19:20,890 --> 00:19:24,260
You can't! You're just barely able to stand!

282
00:19:25,300 --> 00:19:28,430
We have no choice but to leave Droma 
Anim up to Natsu and the others.

283
00:19:29,320 --> 00:19:31,460
We have something we must do.

284
00:19:31,460 --> 00:19:32,690
Something to do?

285
00:19:33,930 --> 00:19:35,620
My final work.

286
00:19:35,920 --> 00:19:39,190
For that, I'll need your help.

287
00:19:46,710 --> 00:19:48,060
Oh, no!

288
00:19:48,060 --> 00:19:49,940
I can hear screams all the way over here!

289
00:19:49,940 --> 00:19:51,130
They caught up to them!

290
00:19:51,130 --> 00:19:52,590
The Royal Army has...

291
00:19:52,590 --> 00:19:54,800
And in so many numbers...

292
00:19:55,250 --> 00:19:56,300
What'll we do?

293
00:19:56,300 --> 00:19:57,950
We must go.

294
00:19:57,950 --> 00:20:01,210
If we don't, then the Exceed are finished!

295
00:20:01,800 --> 00:20:03,570
We'll fight, too!

296
00:20:03,570 --> 00:20:07,430
Yes. We'll protect our homeland!

297
00:20:07,750 --> 00:20:10,580
I've been waiting for you, Scarlet.

298
00:20:11,850 --> 00:20:13,710
Waiting for me?!

299
00:20:17,490 --> 00:20:19,180
Crap, it was a trap!

300
00:20:19,180 --> 00:20:20,230
An ambush?!

301
00:20:20,770 --> 00:20:22,610
Dodge, Legipyon!

302
00:20:33,910 --> 00:20:36,420
Legipyon!!

303
00:20:40,090 --> 00:20:40,840
Happy!

304
00:20:40,840 --> 00:20:43,380
Aye, sir!

305
00:20:43,620 --> 00:20:46,920
Those who turn against the King 
cannot be allowed to live.

306
00:20:46,920 --> 00:20:49,170
I will finish you for good!

307
00:20:49,170 --> 00:20:50,720
I'm getting off onto the ground!

308
00:20:54,730 --> 00:20:57,960
Holding the both of you up is impossible!

309
00:20:58,560 --> 00:21:00,100
Legipyon!

310
00:21:00,100 --> 00:21:03,790
I'm sorry, Carla! And 
would you stop squirming?!

311
00:21:05,150 --> 00:21:06,310
So heavy...

312
00:21:06,310 --> 00:21:08,530
Even though there's only one of me!

313
00:21:11,690 --> 00:21:13,640
Oh yeah, now I'm wondering...

314
00:21:13,640 --> 00:21:14,850
Where's Erza?

315
00:21:25,020 --> 00:21:26,660
Scarlet!

316
00:21:26,660 --> 00:21:29,640
I think it's time we finished 
this, Knightwalker.

317
00:21:34,040 --> 00:21:35,680
Everyone, dismount to the ground!

318
00:21:36,890 --> 00:21:39,040
I'll fight her myself!

319
00:21:39,040 --> 00:21:39,480
Yes, ma'am!

320
00:21:43,940 --> 00:21:46,680
The old capital of those filthy cats?

321
00:21:47,100 --> 00:21:49,360
A fitting place to make your grave.

322
00:21:49,800 --> 00:21:52,200
I say the same back to you.

323
00:21:53,500 --> 00:21:58,370
Even as you are Erza, you have 
hurt Fairy Tail far too much.

324
00:21:59,920 --> 00:22:04,000
Even as you are Erza, you 
have turned against our King.

325
00:22:05,340 --> 00:22:08,170
There's no need for two Erzas.

326
00:22:17,450 --> 00:22:21,730
This fight continues until 
only one of us remains!

327
00:23:56,350 --> 00:23:59,520
Natsu, what does it mean to be alive?

328
00:23:59,520 --> 00:24:01,300
What's this all of a sudden, Happy?

329
00:24:01,300 --> 00:24:02,640
Did you eat something funky?

330
00:24:02,640 --> 00:24:04,420
I'm just like always!

331
00:24:04,420 --> 00:24:06,350
Anyway, what's your answer, Natsu?

332
00:24:06,350 --> 00:24:07,900
It's simple, really.

333
00:24:07,900 --> 00:24:10,620
Living is eatin', sleepin' 
and gettin' into fights!

334
00:24:10,620 --> 00:24:14,340
You're actually quite the philosopher, Natsu.

335
00:24:14,340 --> 00:24:16,970
Next time: Those Who Are Alive.

336
00:24:16,970 --> 00:24:18,850
So, what's your answer, Happy?

337
00:24:18,850 --> 00:24:22,870
Catching fish, cooking fish, 
and eating fish, I suppose.

338
00:24:22,870 --> 00:24:25,080
Pretty much the same things...

